  <td valign=3Dtop style=3D'padding:0cm 5.75pt 0cm 5.75pt'>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>A very hardy, relatively short amphibian being. Thei=
r home
  planet has extreme climate changes because of 2 orbital moons, life on <s=
pan
  class=3DSpellE>Roshar</span> has had to be able to handle many different
  climates.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> are not very =
intelligent
  but are extremely optimistic and naive creatures. Most life on <span
  class=3DSpellE>Roshar</span> evolved to support other life because of such
  adverse conditions, this has made <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span>
  extremely unequipped to mix in the Galaxy because they judge everyone by
  their own standards, finding it extremely hard to imagine other races
  treating them badly despite past experience. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Because of their nature they are a very likeable rac=
e and
  other races all love to trade with <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span>,
  often taking advantage of them. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Extremely positive about their space program, <span
  class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> believe meeting other life can only be a=
 good
  thing for them. All <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> are enthusiast=
ic to
  spread out in the Galaxy. </p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>On <span class=3DSpellE>Roshan</span> all life has a=
 12 year
  metamorphosis cycle because of one of the moons, this still happens
  throughout the Galaxy because each <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshan's</span>
  cycle synchronises with other <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> arou=
nd
  them. Life goes in to a slowed down docile state while each individual
  changes sex and finds a new partner to reproduce.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> use mecha=
nical,
  tentacle like robots for many jobs and have adapted this technology to
  quickly dock, refuel or load ships.<span style=3D'mso-spacerun:yes'>&nbsp;
  </span>The <span class=3DSpellE>Rad</span> Coupler allows for extremely
  efficient docking operations that can be achieved at high speeds.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal><span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> usually stick
  together in large communities, able to easily colonise any water based
  planets.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Tairoshans</span> prefer Fi=
ghters /
  Torpedo Bombers combined with Torpedoes on smaller designs, with an
  Efficiency Energy Research focus.<i style=3D'mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>=
<o:p></o:p></i></p>
  </td>
